@node "inst" "Getting this sod to work..."
(1) Stick all files up yer arse.

(2) Make sure all of these are in C:

    ZIP
    LZX
    LHA
    copy
    makedir
    delete

Few people out there still not aware that LHA and LZX are both
now freeware. On Aminet. Somewhere.

Aminet/comm/utils/gfx/mods/funktracker/scans/net/tcp/lha.zip

Hehehehe. Man, I'm easily amused. Bet you're not.

(3) Read other sections of this docfile.


@endnode
